gomodel:SYNGO_616  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: A total of 296 proteins were identified in a PSD preparation by from forebrain or cerebellum by LC-MS/MS.\nFor proteins coming from datasets derived from PSD (detergent-resistant synaptic junctions) preparations without defined selection / enrichment of the pre- or postsynaptic compartment we cannot assign these proteins to excitatory and/or inhibitory nor to the presynapse or / and postsynapse without further information.. Experimental description: \"PSD fractions were prepared from rat forebrains and cerebellums at 4 °C (22).\" p.1159" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9377-7414" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0269-0311" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9880-1214" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9681-3318" ;
